text: Sofiya Dmitrievna Shishkina (; born 30 September 1998) is a Russian footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Russia women's national team. ==Career== Shishkina has been capped for the Russia national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Russian women's footballers Category:Russia women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Zvezda 2005 Perm players
